{
  "stem": "25591.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't give you the year, but I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whether I was five or seven, I couldn't tell you, but it was at about that stage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a very difficult one to answer because you see, even after the Anschluss, the, the taking of Austria, I did not fully understand what the word Hitler and Nazism meant.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understood the hatred for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I understood the persecution of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understood Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I understood lots of things, but I, I really was part of and, and born into a highly civilized Western European family and culture.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And gas chambers were not part of my, of my, of my scheme or of my framework.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I knew, for instance, that there was such an organization as Hitlerjugend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "An aunt and uncle of mine had a villa up in Buda, and a very large place very near it was taken over for the summer by Hitlerjugend, in the early '40s.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember what year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I saw these German, young boys playing, and exercising, and, and, and being there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I really did not, even at that time, could go down the road all the way to what the Holocaust would mean.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I, I knew it was a, a horrible, vicious, anti-Semitic, anti-democratic, rotten crowd.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I did not dream that would-- it would-- it could go this far.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I very much realized it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I resented it, but I was always very self confident and, and I did not feel inferior.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt excluded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt discriminated against, but I never felt, never for a moment, did I feel inferior.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were situations, there were situations, which were frightening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jews being beaten up.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
